        "MEDIUM: No in-flight / processing gauge. Cannot distinguish 'idle because no work' from 'stuck because deadlocked'.",
        "MEDIUM: billing_api_duration_seconds histogram exists but no SLO-derived latency alert (e.g., p99 > threshold that would threaten the 1-hour window under load)"
